Executive Profile
Ronald B. Maggard Sr.Director, J. Alexander's Holdings, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 5 different industries.See Board Relationships67$108,700
Background

		Mr. Ronald B. Maggard, Sr., Co-Founded Maggard Enterprises, Inc., a franchisee of Long John Silver and A&W restaurants in 1970 and has been its Chairman of the Board and President since 1972. Mr. Maggard serves as President of Midstate Distributing, a miller distributing company, based in Lexington, Kentucky. He has been a franchisee of quick-service restaurants for over 30 years. He was employed at QSR industry. He served as Chairman of the Board at Checker's/Rally's. ... He has been a Director of J. Alexander's Holdings, Inc since September 14, 2015. He serves as a Director of HyperActive Technologies, Inc. Mr. Maggard served as an Independent Director of CKE Restaurants Inc., since March 2003. He served as a Director of Santa Barbara Restaurant Group, Inc., ("SBRG") and Checkers Drive-In Restaurants Inc., until 2002. He served as Director of Carl Karcher Enterprises. He has been a Director of  J. Alexander's Holdings, Inc since September 14, 2015.Read Full Background




