Insider Activity


Individual




Ronald B. Maggard



Mr. Ronald B. Maggard, Sr., is Co-Founder at Maggard Enterprises, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at J. Alexander's Holdings, Inc., American Blue Ribbon Holdings, Inc. and HyperActive Technologies, Inc. Mr. Maggard was previously employed as Chairman by Checkers Drive-In Restaurants, Inc. and Chairman by Rally's Hamburgers, Inc. He also served on the board at Carl Karcher Enterprises LLC, CKE Restaurants, Inc. and Santa Barbara Restaurant Group LLC.



